  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: You are asking dangerous questions with the confidence of someone who has
      not yet paid for them.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Fine. Start with the greenhouse. Then leave my conscience out of it.
  choices:
  - choiceText: That is more than enough. Thank you.
